ass=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h6 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Residency By Investment<\/h6>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2163e90a elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"2163e90a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;xpro-anim-mask-from-left&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h1 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">PORTUGAL D8 VISA<\/h1>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-48b07098 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"48b07098\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;xpro-anim-mask-from-left&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Portugal \u2013 A Business Haven for Investors &amp; Entrepreneurs.<br>\nPortugal D8 Visa- Best Opportunity for Digital Nomads.<br>\nLooking for an Upgrade in Life, D8 Nomad Visa is the Answer.\n<\/h4>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-22bef357 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-child\" data-id=\"22bef357\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-70b3b42a elementor-align-left elementor-widget__width-auto elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"70b3b42a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;xpro-anim-mask-from-left&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-lg\" href=\"https:\/\/forecastmigration.com\/contact-us\/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-icon\">\n\t\t\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"icon icon-phone1\"><\/i>\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">Get a Consultation<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-64ad6a1f e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"64ad6a1f\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-33598d67 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"33598d67\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-467fc6f3 elementor-widget__width-auto elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"467fc6f3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;xpro-anim-mask-from-left&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h6 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Processing Timeline: 4-6 Months<br>\nResidency Permit Duration: 1 Year but Extendable <\/h6>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2e53855a elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"2e53855a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;xpro-anim-mask-from-left&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Portugal D8 Visa- Best Opportunity for Digital Nomads <\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a5d0c77 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"a5d0c77\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2f995c01 elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2f995c01\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;xpro-anim-mask-from-left&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>The D8 visa, officially known as the &#8220;Temporary Residence Visa for the Exercise of Professional Activity Provided Remotely Outside the National Territory,&#8221; allows non-EU\/EEA citizens with remote jobs to live and work in Portugal for up to one year, with the possibility of renewal and even permanent residency after five years. Since 2022, Portugal&#8217;s new digital nomad visa enables remote workers and freelancers to establish residency by demonstrating a monthly income of at least \u20ac3,480 and maintaining savings of at least \u20ac36,480. The individuals who want to explore work possibilities in Portugal, D8 Visa is a suitable option in terms of affordability as well.<br \/>With D8 Digital Nomad Visa, you can at least get access to a country that is safe and has a growing economy. It will be easier for applicants to unlock more horizons while sustaining their remote jobs. All these immigration streams in D category including D2, D7, D8 and D10 have entirely different target audience. Some are for investors and entrepreneurs and others are for talented professionals who have skillset but cannot afford huge investments.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-63c0101 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"63c0101\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ff3d1c3 elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ff3d1c3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;xpro-anim-mask-from-left&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h4><strong>Eligibility Criteria: <\/strong><\/h4>\n<ul>\n \t<li>The applicant must be non-EU national<\/li>\n \t<li>Must be above 18 years of age<\/li>\n \t<li>Able to fulfill income requirement<\/li>\n \t<li>Applicant must have a clean criminal background<\/li>\n \t<li>Must have a health insurance that covers the stay in Portugal<\/li>\n<\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-21bd00d7 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"21bd00d7\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-50833d33 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-child\" data-id=\"50833d33\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3e16c565 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"3e16c565\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Step by Step Processing \u2013 Understanding D8 Visa <\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2bbd1bef elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2bbd1bef\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Don\u2019t miss the chance to live in Portugal, the land of opportunities for better a quality of lifestyle and favorable business environment.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-51def7dc e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-child\" data-id=\"51def7dc\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5150832f e-grid e-con-full e-con e-child\" data-id=\"5150832f\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5c1f609f ekit-equal-height-enable elementor-widget__width-inherit elementor-widget-laptop__width-inherit elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-elementskit-icon-box\" data-id=\"5c1f609f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;xpro-anim-mask-from-left&quot;,&quot;_animation_delay&quot;:1}\" data-widget_type=\"elementskit-icon-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"ekit-wid-con\" >        <!-- link opening -->\n                <!-- end link opening -->\n\n        <div class=\"elementskit-infobox text-left text-left icon-top-align elementor-animation-  gradient-active  hover_from_left\">\n                            <div class=\"elementskit-box-header\">\n                <div class=\"elementskit-info-box-icon \">\n                    <img decoding=\"async\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" src=\"https:\/\/forecastmigration.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/better-health.png\" class=\"attachment- size-\" alt=\"\" \/>                <\/div>\n          <\/div>\n                <div class=\"box-body\">\n                            <h3 class=\"elementskit-info-box-title\">\n                    Prepare and Compile Documents                <\/h3>\n                        \t\t  \t<p>1.\tValid Passport <br>\n2.\tProof of Income <br>\n3.\tProof of Accommodation in Portugal <br>\n4.\tHeath Insurance  <br>\n5.\tPolice Character Certificate <br>\n<\/p>\n                                <\/div>\n        \n        \n                <\/div>\n        <\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-687caf33 ekit-equal-height-enable elementor-widget__width-inherit elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-elementskit-icon-box\" data-id=\"687caf33\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;xpro-anim-mask-from-left&quot;,&quot;_animation_delay&quot;:1}\" data-widget_type=\"elementskit-icon-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"ekit-wid-con\" >        <!-- link opening -->\n                <!-- end link opening -->\n\n        <div class=\"elementskit-infobox text-left text-left icon-top-align elementor-animation-  gradient-active  hover_from_left\">\n                            <div class=\"elementskit-box-header\">\n                <div class=\"elementskit-info-box-icon \">\n                    <img decoding=\"async\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" src=\"https:\/\/forecastmigration.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/job-opportunities.png\" class=\"attachment- size-\" alt=\"\" \/>                <\/div>\n          <\/div>\n                <div class=\"box-body\">\n                            <h3 class=\"elementskit-info-box-title\">\n                    Application Submission                <\/h3>\n                        \t\t  \t<p>1.\tCompletion of Digital Nomad Form with correct information <br>\n2.\tThe Application fee will be paid which is around EUR 800<br>\n3.\tSubmission of form and accompanying documents to Portuguese Embassy<br>\n<\/p>\n                                <\/div>\n        \n        \n                <\/div>\n        <\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6df08929 ekit-equal-height-enable elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-elementskit-icon-box\" data-id=\"6df08929\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;xpro-anim-mask-from-left&quot;,&quot;_animation_delay&quot;:1}\" data-widget_type=\"elementskit-icon-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"ekit-wid-con\" >        <!-- link opening -->\n                <!-- end link opening -->\n\n        <div class=\"elementskit-infobox text-left text-left icon-top-align elementor-animation-  gradient-active  hover_from_left\">\n                            <div class=\"elementskit-box-header\">\n                <div class=\"elementskit-info-box-icon \">\n                    <img decoding=\"async\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" src=\"https:\/\/forecastmigration.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/support-1.png\" class=\"attachment- size-\" alt=\"\" \/>                <\/div>\n          <\/div>\n                <div class=\"box-body\">\n                            <h3 class=\"elementskit-info-box-title\">\n                    Visa Processing                <\/h3>\n                        \t\t  \t<p>The application review process will take 60-120 days and applicant will be informed via email on the status (Approval or Rejection) of Digital nomad visa.<\/p>\n                                <\/div>\n        \n        \n                <\/div>\n        <\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1a6289a3 ekit-equal-height-enable elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-elementskit-icon-box\" data-id=\"1a6289a3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;xpro-anim-mask-from-left&quot;,&quot;_animation_delay&quot;:1}\" data-widget_type=\"elementskit-icon-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"ekit-wid-con\" >        <!-- link opening -->\n                <!-- end link opening -->\n\n        <div class=\"elementskit-infobox text-left text-left icon-top-align elementor-animation-  gradient-active  hover_from_left\">\n                            <div class=\"elementskit-box-header\">\n                <div class=\"elementskit-info-box-icon \">\n                    <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" src=\"https:\/\/forecastmigration.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/peace-flag.png\" class=\"attachment- size-\" alt=\"\" \/>                <\/div>\n          <\/div>\n                <div class=\"box-body\">\n                            <h3 class=\"elementskit-info-box-title\">\n                    Plan your Stay in Portugal                <\/h3>\n                        \t\t  \t<p>Applicants must need to show a proof of accommodation, a place where they will be living in Portugal for 1 year. The income proof is also considerable to understand if an applicant can manage cost of living in Portugal or not. \n\u2022\tMinimum Accommodation Cost: \u20ac600 \u2013 \u20ac1000 <br>\n\u2022\tUtilities &amp; Groceries: \u20ac400 \u2013 \u20ac600<br>\n\u2022\tInternet and Call plans: \u20ac30 \u2013 \u20ac50<br>\n\u2022\tPublic transportation pass: \u20ac40 \u2013 \u20ac60<br>\n<\/p>\n                                <\/div>\n        \n        \n                <\/div>\n        <\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t